{
  "stem": "4963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Red Cross would stop by, and I remember that very distinctly, and start calling out names for packages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we got packages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember opening up-- in fact, it was a brown package with string around, and-- and you know, saying, from my father, there was a note there saying, you know, this is something for you.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I love you, and so on, and signed my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were cookies and candy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we were really just overjoyed with all this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, after a few days, we were taken by buses, and we went back to Kovno.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, at the station, my aunts were there to meet me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, well, what happened?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are my parents?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, well, why don't you come to the house and we'll tell you?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then they told me the story that my parents were sent out and that, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they really forged my parents' name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They signed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't want to alarm me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, later on, I found out my Aunt Paula was really the one who was instrumental to bring all the children back from the-- from the Palanga, from the camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it weren't for my aunt, perhaps they might have even annihilated all of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she risked her life to go out and-- and round the parents up so that-- through the Red Cross, so that the children would-- should be able to come back.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
